{"tid":2452220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局或要求所有香港資助大學將《港區國安法》教育列為必修","createTime":"2021-03-18T16:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T07:16:20.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2392acdd93f1a0acc8b7d6b6d15cf904e03a91d5","tid":2452220,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:41:00.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄早前稱，已與數名資助大學校長會面，商討如何在校内推行《國安法》教育。《立場新聞》今（18日）引述消息指，教資會就2022至2025年度學額分配計劃向院校發出「啟動籌劃信件」（Start Letter），列明「宏觀規劃指標」，當中要求將《港區國安法》、憲法及《基本法》教育列為必修，教育局局長楊潤雄更有出席上月討論有關議題的教資會會議，惟信件及會上均未有建議納入必修的具體形式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/PVQR7IF2OZBZTOB45T34UURXIU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR38pbfuMiTWcw6uBKB-sRok-9QWizC8Bu7RKI8qh9fgNby32SvE2ij6VnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FPVQR7IF2OZBZTOB45T34UURXIU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR38pbfuMiTWcw6uBKB-sRok-9QWizC8Bu7RKI8qh9fgNby32SvE2ij6VnI&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=319e1d94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210318%2FPVQR7IF2OZBZTOB45T34UURXIU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR38pbfuMiTWcw6uBKB-sRok-9QWizC8Bu7RKI8qh9fgNby32SvE2ij6VnI&h=8bf1d654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210318/PVQR7IF2OZBZTOB45T34UURXIU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR38pbfuMiTWcw6uBKB-sRok-9QWizC8Bu7RKI8qh9fgNby32SvE2ij6VnI</a>"},{"pid":"6b0c39e184b9a6c8431b0b652994c52a7c231f67","tid":2452220,"uid":7179,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16: